foods.ingredients: DICED TOMATOES (TOMATOES, TOMATO JUICE, CITRIC ACID, CALCIUM CHLORIDE), CREAM, SKIM MILK, BLACK BEAN, WATER, CHEDDAR CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES, ANNATTO [COLOR], NATAMYCIN [NATURAL MOLD INHIBITOR]), TOMATO PASTE, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, INVERT SUGAR, SALT, DEHYDRATED ONION & GARLIC, ONION, CILANTRO, JALAPENO PEPPER, CULTURED SKIM MILK, SPICE, GELATIN, LACTIC & CITRIC ACID, GARLIC, MILK PROTEIN ISOLATE, XANTHAN GUM, WHITE CORN FLOUR, DEHYDRATED GREEN BELL PEPPER, MONO & DIGLYCERIDES, ACETIC ACID, CITRUS FIBER, LIME JUICE CONCENTRATE, CORN FIBER, DEXTROSE, PAPRIKA (COLOR), DISODIUM PHOSPHATE, LEMON JUICE CONCENTRATE, NATURAL FLAVOR, WHITE VINEGAR, LOCUST BEAN GUM, TOMATO POWDER, GUAR GUM, SOYBEAN OIL, CALCIUM CHLORIDE, FERROUS GLUCONATE (COLOR), MALTODEXTRIN, EXTRACTIVES OF PAPRIKA, VINEGAR SOLIDS.
